[
    {
        "text": "So ladies and gentlemen, at TED we talk a lot about leadership and how to make a movement.",
        "startTime": 1997,
        "endTime": 6400,
        "slowStartTime": 3145,
        "slowEndTime": 9825
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's watch a movement happen, from start to finish, in under three minutes...",
        "startTime": 6782,
        "endTime": 10105,
        "slowStartTime": 10323,
        "slowEndTime": 15382
    },
    {
        "text": "...and dissect some lessons from it.",
        "startTime": 10224,
        "endTime": 11619,
        "slowStartTime": 15486,
        "slowEndTime": 17654
    },
    {
        "text": "First of course you know, a leader needs the guts to stand out and be ridiculed.",
        "startTime": 12279,
        "endTime": 16857,
        "slowStartTime": 18568,
        "slowEndTime": 25511
    },
    {
        "text": "But what he's doing is so easy to follow.",
        "startTime": 18908,
        "endTime": 20719,
        "slowStartTime": 28512,
        "slowEndTime": 31303
    },
    {
        "text": "So, here's his first follower with a crucial role.",
        "startTime": 20830,
        "endTime": 22865,
        "slowStartTime": 31395,
        "slowEndTime": 34523
    },
    {
        "text": "He's going to show everyone else how to follow.",
        "startTime": 23037,
        "endTime": 25005,
        "slowStartTime": 34705,
        "slowEndTime": 37733
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, notice that the leader embraces him as an equal.",
        "startTime": 25536,
        "endTime": 27779,
        "slowStartTime": 38454,
        "slowEndTime": 41893
    },
    {
        "text": "So, now it's not about the leader anymore; it's about them, plural.",
        "startTime": 28044,
        "endTime": 31373,
        "slowStartTime": 42216,
        "slowEndTime": 47285
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, there he is calling to his friends.",
        "startTime": 31739,
        "endTime": 33459,
        "slowStartTime": 47758,
        "slowEndTime": 50413
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, if you notice that the first follower is actually an underestimated form of leadership in itself.",
        "startTime": 33889,
        "endTime": 38927,
        "slowStartTime": 50983,
        "slowEndTime": 58615
    },
    {
        "text": "It takes guts to stand out like that.",
        "startTime": 39308,
        "endTime": 41017,
        "slowStartTime": 59112,
        "slowEndTime": 61750
    },
    {
        "text": "The first follower is what transforms a lone nut into a leader.",
        "startTime": 41811,
        "endTime": 46098,
        "slowStartTime": 62867,
        "slowEndTime": 69372
    },
    {
        "text": "And here comes a second follower.",
        "startTime": 51704,
        "endTime": 53168,
        "slowStartTime": 77706,
        "slowEndTime": 79977
    },
    {
        "text": "Now it's not a lone nut, it's not two nuts; three is a crowd and a crowd is news.",
        "startTime": 53536,
        "endTime": 58134,
        "slowStartTime": 80454,
        "slowEndTime": 87426
    },
    {
        "text": "So, a movement must be public.",
        "startTime": 58425,
        "endTime": 60312,
        "slowStartTime": 87788,
        "slowEndTime": 90693
    },
    {
        "text": "It's important to show not just the leader, but the followers...",
        "startTime": 60731,
        "endTime": 63786,
        "slowStartTime": 91247,
        "slowEndTime": 95904
    },
    {
        "text": "...because you find that new followers emulate the followers, not the leader.",
        "startTime": 63966,
        "endTime": 67641,
        "slowStartTime": 96099,
        "slowEndTime": 101687
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, here come two more people and immediately after, three more people.",
        "startTime": 68331,
        "endTime": 71787,
        "slowStartTime": 102646,
        "slowEndTime": 107905
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we've got momentum.",
        "startTime": 72034,
        "endTime": 73261,
        "slowStartTime": 108201,
        "slowEndTime": 110117
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the tipping point.",
        "startTime": 73388,
        "endTime": 74549,
        "slowStartTime": 110232,
        "slowEndTime": 112048
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we've got a movement.",
        "startTime": 74620,
        "endTime": 76135,
        "slowStartTime": 112080,
        "slowEndTime": 114427
    },
    {
        "text": "So notice that as more people join in, it's less risky.",
        "startTime": 77957,
        "endTime": 81636,
        "slowStartTime": 117086,
        "slowEndTime": 122679
    },
    {
        "text": "So, those that were sitting on the fence before now have no reason not to.",
        "startTime": 81842,
        "endTime": 85263,
        "slowStartTime": 122913,
        "slowEndTime": 128120
    },
    {
        "text": "They won't stand out,...",
        "startTime": 85747,
        "endTime": 86875,
        "slowStartTime": 128770,
        "slowEndTime": 130537
    },
    {
        "text": "...they won't be ridiculed...",
        "startTime": 87607,
        "endTime": 88877,
        "slowStartTime": 131560,
        "slowEndTime": 133541
    },
    {
        "text": "...but they will be part of the in-crowd if they hurry.",
        "startTime": 89108,
        "endTime": 91437,
        "slowStartTime": 133812,
        "slowEndTime": 137381
    },
    {
        "text": "So over the next minute, you'll see all of those that prefer to stick with the crowd...",
        "startTime": 91968,
        "endTime": 98630,
        "slowStartTime": 138102,
        "slowEndTime": 148170
    },
    {
        "text": "...because eventually they would be ridiculed for not joining in...",
        "startTime": 98713,
        "endTime": 101732,
        "slowStartTime": 148219,
        "slowEndTime": 152823
    },
    {
        "text": "...and that's how you make a movement.",
        "startTime": 102252,
        "endTime": 103799,
        "slowStartTime": 153528,
        "slowEndTime": 155923
    },
    {
        "text": "But let's recap some lessons from this.",
        "startTime": 104246,
        "endTime": 106265,
        "slowStartTime": 156519,
        "slowEndTime": 159623
    },
    {
        "text": "So first, if you are the type like the shirtless dancing guy that is standing alone,...",
        "startTime": 106923,
        "endTime": 112145,
        "slowStartTime": 160534,
        "slowEndTime": 168442
    },
    {
        "text": "...remember the importance of nurturing your first few followers as equals...",
        "startTime": 112301,
        "endTime": 115899,
        "slowStartTime": 168601,
        "slowEndTime": 174073
    },
    {
        "text": "...so it's clearly about the movement, not you.",
        "startTime": 116265,
        "endTime": 118541,
        "slowStartTime": 174548,
        "slowEndTime": 178036
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, but we might have missed the real lesson here.",
        "startTime": 120023,
        "endTime": 122495,
        "slowStartTime": 180184,
        "slowEndTime": 183968
    },
    {
        "text": "The biggest lesson if you noticed, did you catch it?",
        "startTime": 122577,
        "endTime": 125237,
        "slowStartTime": 184015,
        "slowEndTime": 188081
    },
    {
        "text": "Is that leadership is over - glorified...",
        "startTime": 125826,
        "endTime": 128167,
        "slowStartTime": 188889,
        "slowEndTime": 192475
    },
    {
        "text": "...that yes, it was the shirtless guy was first and he'll get all the credit.",
        "startTime": 129048,
        "endTime": 132193,
        "slowStartTime": 193722,
        "slowEndTime": 198514
    },
    {
        "text": "But it was really the first follower that transformed the lone nut into a leader.",
        "startTime": 132569,
        "endTime": 137251,
        "slowStartTime": 199004,
        "slowEndTime": 206101
    },
    {
        "text": "So, as we're told that we should all be leaders, that would be really ineffective.",
        "startTime": 137785,
        "endTime": 141205,
        "slowStartTime": 206828,
        "slowEndTime": 212032
    },
    {
        "text": "If you really care about starting a movement,...",
        "startTime": 141825,
        "endTime": 143697,
        "slowStartTime": 212888,
        "slowEndTime": 215770
    },
    {
        "text": "...have the courage to follow and show others how to follow.",
        "startTime": 144099,
        "endTime": 147137,
        "slowStartTime": 216298,
        "slowEndTime": 220931
    },
    {
        "text": "And when you find a lone nut doing something great,...",
        "startTime": 147493,
        "endTime": 149742,
        "slowStartTime": 221389,
        "slowEndTime": 224838
    },
    {
        "text": "...have the guts to be the first one to stand up and join in.",
        "startTime": 150052,
        "endTime": 153195,
        "slowStartTime": 225228,
        "slowEndTime": 230018
    },
    {
        "text": "And what a perfect place to do that, at TED.",
        "startTime": 153509,
